<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Georg Zollner von Rottenstein</head><p>Der Rat versichert die Freundschaft nach Freilassung der Armleute des Konrad Paumgartner und Georg Rummel, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_147" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_147_r1l1">Gorgen Cʒollner </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l2">vom Rotenſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_147_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg Als vvir hanſen Göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l4">nehſt cʒu euch geſant heten / von Conrad Paum = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l5">gartners vnd Görgen Rumels <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l6">vnd ~ <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> Armenlewte wegen . die Jr gefangen het </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l7">Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns dy <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l8">fürbraht . vvie Jr <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ ir Armlewte von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> bete wegen <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ledig vnd loſe gelaſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l10">habt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">des vvir euch gut <expan>freutlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> danken </del> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l11">alſo bedürfft Jr euch 
<del rend="strikethrough">darümb </del> von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l12">wegen keins argen gen vns <expan>verſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvo vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l13">euch lieb oder dinſte beweiſen möhten das <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l14"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Margarete </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_147" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Gorgen Czollner vom Rotenstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg, als wir Hansen Göldlein,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, nehst czu euch gesant heten
                        von Conrad Paumgartners und Görgen Rumels <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> armenlewte
                        wegen, die ir gefangen het, also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns dy
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbraht, wie ir
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir armlewte von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> bete wegen
                            <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ledig und lose gelassen habt; und also
                        bedürfft ir euch von <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache wegen keins
                        argen gen uns <expan>verseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wo wir euch lieb oder dinste beweisen möhten, das
                            <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
                        Margarete.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
